$date
  2026-06-07T00:00:00.000Z
$end
$version
  WaveCrux Pro board demo fixture generator
$end
$comment
  Digilent Nexys Video out-of-box demo — individual per-bit signals.
  LED show: cylon / VU bar / chase / switch-mirror / expand / sparkle.
  Live peripherals: HDMI raster, audio sine, ADC, etc.
  Re-generate with `dart run tool/generate_board_demo_fixtures.dart`.
$end
$timescale 1 ns $end
$scope module top $end
$var wire 1 ! led0 $end
$var wire 1 " led1 $end
$var wire 1 # led2 $end
$var wire 1 $ led3 $end
$var wire 1 % led4 $end
$var wire 1 & led5 $end
$var wire 1 ' led6 $end
$var wire 1 ( led7 $end
$var wire 1 ) sw0 $end
$var wire 1 * sw1 $end
$var wire 1 + sw2 $end
$var wire 1 , sw3 $end
$var wire 1 - sw4 $end
$var wire 1 . sw5 $end
$var wire 1 / sw6 $end
$var wire 1 0 sw7 $end
$var wire 1 1 btnC $end
$var wire 1 2 btnU $end
$var wire 1 3 btnL $end
$var wire 1 4 btnR $end
$var wire 1 5 btnD $end
$var wire 16 6 hdmi_in_data $end
$var wire 1 7 hdmi_in_pixel_clk $end
$var wire 1 8 hdmi_in_hsync $end
$var wire 1 9 hdmi_in_vsync $end
$var wire 1 : hdmi_in_de $end
$var wire 16 ; hdmi_out_data $end
$var wire 1 < hdmi_out_pixel_clk $end
$var wire 1 = hdmi_out_hsync $end
$var wire 1 > hdmi_out_vsync $end
$var wire 1 ? hdmi_out_de $end
$var wire 16 @ oled $end
$var wire 16 A audio_codec $end
$upscope $end
$enddefinitions $end
